[WARNING: This project is not yet ready for proper use. Its very much an alpha at the moment]

Dependencies: (Jruby 1.6.1 or greater)

*** Installation (Assuming jruby is your default)

$ gem install jsmetric4java


*** Usage

Cyclometric complexity for a file:
$ jsmetric4java path_to_js_file

Cyclometric complexity for all .js files in a Directory
$ jsmetric4java path_to_dir


*** Usage with JRUBY 
 
Download Jruby 1.6.x (http://www.jruby.org/download)
Extract JRuby into a directory.
Add that directory's bin subdirectory to the end of your path.

Test it: 
$ jruby -v

Install Jsmetric4Java
$ jruby -S gem install jsmetric4java

Use Jsmetric4java
$ jsmetric4java path/to/js/dir